Nene: Me too... I kinda feel braver than before.
Nene: Um... Thank you for letting me join.
An: Don't mention it, Kusanagi! I had fun singing with you!
Shiho: Yeah, you sang really well.
Nene: Oh...
An: Alright, I think it's about time we wrapped up. Thanks for doing this with me, you two!
An: And Hinomori, thank you for everything else today.
Shiho: *Nod*
